This workspace contains multiple repositories:

- `web`: Django web app and shared backend services for Camera Roll Sounds.
- `camera-roll-sounds-api`: Image-to-audio processing API package for Camera Roll Sounds.
- `camera-roll-sounds-ios`: Native iOS app for Camera Roll Sounds.
- `camera-roll-sounds-react`: React frontend for Camera Roll Sounds.
- `ios-shared`: Shared SwiftUI authentication and account components used by the iOS app.
